Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000117
Properties.Text: Aydys! Fetch me the three tallest loamsprouts! Quickly now!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Oskol's mother must be sick again. I'd best hurry.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Loamsprouts are green, bulbous fungi which grow on long stalks. They taste terrible, but they make good medicine.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: I'll find them at the back of the cellar, in the long trough.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Our own little treasure trove. But the loamsprouts aren't here.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000011B
Properties.Text: [A delightful assortment of mushrooms grows here in the darkness. Some treat stubborn ailments; some treat a rumbling stomach.]

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000011B
Properties.Text: [The mushrooms rest here, safe and snug.]

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: They're fascinating, but I need to find the loamsprouts: tall with green bulbs.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000011B
Properties.Text: [The light catches the gleam of a toadstool like the eye of a cat. Is it giving you an impatient glance?]

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: I'll be in trouble if I don't find the loamsprouts soon! Long stalks, green globes...

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000011B
Properties.Text: [A snatch of conversation from outside comes through the wall here, making it seem as though the mushrooms are gossipping.]

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: I'll really be for it if I don't get those loamsprouts from the back of the cellar right now!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000011B
Properties.Text: [The noise of the street is louder now. Are the mushrooms disappointed in the amount of time you have wasted?]

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: I'm going to be in so much trouble!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000117
Properties.Text: Ah! Just in time! Quickly now.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000153
Properties.Text: [The loamsprouts poke contentedly from the bed, their objectionable smell disguised by the rich earthiness of the cellar.]

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Here we are!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: And not a moment too soon! I'd best hurry upstairs before it's too late.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000153
Properties.Text: [Aydys twists three loamsprouts delicately from the soil.]

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000117
Properties.Text: Aydys! What took you so long? The mixture is starting to turn!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Here you are!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: I'm so sorry, I -

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000117
Properties.Text: Just give me the sprouts! I'll deal with you later.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Here.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000117
Properties.Text: What are you doing, Aydys! I need those loamsprouts now!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000010F
Properties.Text: Sorry! I'll be right back.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000117
Properties.Text: [Dolaana twists the stems of the loamsprouts and places them into the pot, whispering as she does so.]
